parameters:
Fotizona Guard: Surprising, isn't it, having female guards?
We have confidence that we can outmatch any ordinary man.

Fotizona Guard: Just between us, the security here is easy.
I used to be at the campus, but it was tough with all the
thieves.

Fotizona Guard: To be honest, guarding here is easy. I used
to be at the campus, but it was tough with all the thieves.

Fotizona Guard: No problems today! I pray that days like
this will continue forever.

Fotizona Guard: No problems today! I pray that days like
this will continue forever.

Fotizona Guard: In the treasure chest over there is a
treasure book... Oh my! I shouldn't have spoken to such a
beautiful lady.

Fotizona Guard: In the treasure chest over there is a
treasure book... Oh my! I shouldn't have been talking to
such a beautiful lady.
Clea: Are you Mr. Coke, the client?

Fortizona Guard: Hey hey, are you meeting up? Keep it
moderate since I'm on duty.

Guard Coke: Cut out the weird jokes. We're just friends.
I'll go talk to them for a bit.
Guard Coke: Sorry, but please come with me outside.

Guard Cork: Campus security is tight, so please don't do
anything reckless, okay?
Clea: Sorry to keep you waiting. This is the requested bag.
Guard Cork: Thank you, this is indeed my bag.
Guard Cork: Just to be sure, let me check the contents.

Guard Cork: It's the same as your loincloth, a symbol of the
thief guild, it used to be our pride...

Guard Cork: I disposed of my weapons and armor, but I just
couldn't bring myself to throw this away.
Thief Nora: Are you going to throw that away...?

Guard Cork: Ah, I've made up my mind. It took some time, but
I will continue to live as a guard.

Thief Nora: It's a bold request, but if it's unwanted, would
you mind if I take care of it?

Thief Nora: If you ever feel nostalgic for it, I'll return
it to you.
Guard Cork: I guess that's impossible.
Thief Nora: Y-Yes, you're right, I'm sorry!

Guard Cork: If you're willing to take it, I'll give it to
you.
Thief Nora: T-Thank you very much!

Guard Cork: This is the promised reward. That was a quick
resolution, though.

Guard Cork: As long as there's an Adventurer's Guild, the
Fotizona guards will have an easy time.
Guard Coke: I feel much better now, thank you so much.
